4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 20}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你遇见过最「封面欺诈」的游戏是哪一款？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "比如龙背上的骑兵... 严重不符合"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-cdb1f61ad9a6d6b2061d2529e2a4d9e2_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "66 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2019193198237460044"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIkOKR6J/b8oxcEAMaCTExODg1OTg0OCCVlIDOBjAAOB9AGXITMjAxOTE5MzE5ODIzNzQ2MDA0NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1781525682.642723", "card_id": "Q_2049473848026686184", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 46}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "大麦总裁称《给阿嬷的情书》大爆有偶然性，但很难复制，因永远不知道观众下一部想看什么，如何看待这一说法？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "上海国际电影节 上海国际电影节主论坛上，大麦娱乐总裁李捷表示，他最近经常被问大麦是怎么发掘《给阿嬷的情书》这样的好项目的： 我也想在今天感谢大家对这部电影的支持，它有一定的偶然性、且它复制的可能性，我不知道会有多大。 在这个过程中，我有一些反思，就是过去十年，我们其实一直在找电影投资的方法论。但是大多数方法论都是事后总结出来。我们以前有题材、有类型，制作成本，但是今天我想电影市场经历了很多很大的变化。 我的一个深刻的反思是，我们其实是无法把握观众下一步到底想看什么，这也是过去几年电影市场曲线变化很大的原因，是因为我们在很多投资和电影的创作中，是相信用方法论，我们相信大制作大的演员可以带来观众的看电影的兴趣。 李捷也表示：我们一定要敬畏观众的审美的变化，他们永远在我们之前，我们所有总结的都是事后的方法，但是可能我可以这么说，暑期观众想看什么，我猜测不出来，但是我觉得可能每部成功的电影背后最底层的是真诚，就是那种诚意满满，观众看到了这部电影创作尊重了我，对得起我花的电影票，我进来没有觉得被割韭菜或者是被欺骗。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-3210afc8cf8f819db1eeddbf5db3c731.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "66 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2049473848026686184"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIkOKR6J/b8oxcEAMaCTExOTk3Mzg0NiCi5rjRBjAAODVAGnITMjA0OTQ3Mzg0ODAyNjY4NjE4NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1781525682.644531", "card_id": "Q_2040945350094092194", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 26}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么孩子比成年人的想象力更丰富？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "比如孩子看云可以很容易就想象到它与什么东西有关系，比如像船的云、像冰激凌的云…而大多数成年人看到的云只是云。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-e8db1ba077616222fecb9c0ab33ba747_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "65 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2040945350094092194"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIkOKR6J/b8oxcEAMaCTExOTYwNjU1MiDa2LzQBjAAOCFAG3ITMjA0MDk0NTM1MDA5NDA5MjE5NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1781525682.645226", "card_id": "Q_2022993891255689222", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 23}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么你学了很多认知方法，却依然用不出来？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "看了很多认知升级的书，学了很多思维模型，但遇到实际问题还是不知道该用哪个…到底哪里出了问题？有没有人能系统地解释一下？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "65 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2022993891255689222"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIkOKR6J/b8oxcEAMaCTExODk5MjUxNiDBu7fOBjAAOC9AHHITMjAyMjk5Mzg5MTI1NTY4OTIyMngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1781525682.645971", "card_id": "Q_2047632554103256881", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 27}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你们为什么开始喜欢《泰坦尼克号》里面的贵族少爷卡尔？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "你们为什么开始喜欢《泰坦尼克号》里面的贵族少爷卡尔？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-bd599ab21ea2379432a982b82bba8fe0_b.jpg"}, "met